{
  "stem": "18470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 236.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a roll call one morning, and by sheer accident, the two guys who were standing next to me-- one on the left, one on the right-- were just a few seconds late-- not minutes-- seconds late.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, both of them were beaten to death on the spot for this infringement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I walked away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now that's how terror works also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's haphazard.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's on the one hand, there's premeditation and predictability.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "On the other hand, terror strikes, and that was also very calculated as part of the policy of terror.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was all over place all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for a while, there was a Hebrew teacher who came in, Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Zelligman, and he stopped coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a time when the nuns could no longer offer me schooling either.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were under tremendous pressure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So by the time we left, and I found in our-- my passport-- we left Germany via Hamburg on June 13, 1939.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was on a train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were quite happy, my mother and I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at the very last moment, as we were going on the gangplank, see the-- if you got halfway up to the gangplank plus one step you were, so to speak, under the protection of the ship, which was the SS Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "American ship.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they literally pulled her off the gangplank, and gave her a body search, to make sure that she was not carrying any valuables out of the country.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now as absurdities go, my grandfather, on his bar mitzvah, had received a gold dollar from a relative in America.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they sewed that into my lederhosen strap.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
